idFORGE Framework provides automation scripts and templates to help
you reproduce an specific organization's visual identity manual and
its implementation.

See idforge(1) for more information.

Recent updates for idFORGE Framework are published from time to time
in <http://wiki.centos.org/ArtWork/Framework>.

Discussion about idFORGE Framework take place at CentOS Developers
mailing list <centos-devel@centos.org>.

idFORGE Framework is written by Alain Reguera Delgado
<alain.reguera@gmail.com>

idFORGE Framework is copyright of The CentOS Artwork SIG and released
as free software. See the LICENSE file for more information about
copying matters.
